Nodes.Comment: Follow the route closely to the Vista to avoid an invisible wall.
If event is up take middle option and move on, otherwise collect Eggs and turn in to Roosts.
Kill animals, cuddle the cubs at the Heart NPC.
You can [weapon-swap] cuddle the cubs if you're not transformed.
[Weapon-swap] open the cages, kill Banners and Svanir.
Go East into the cave to complete the Heart, come back when you're done.
You can cancel the paint removal by moving.
Pick up a Bag, wait for rabbits to spawn, drop, scare it, repeat.
Throw Snowballs at children, aim slightly behind them. Do event if it's up.
Continue North to complete the Heart. Use the Waypoint when done.
Do event if it's up. If not, carry kegs or water sleeping NPCs.
Get the POI from here, don't enter instance.
Jump to these next two nodes.
Grab a Rabbit from the hole.
Kill a Rock Dog to finish the Heart.
